{"about_the_game":"In <strong>Roguelike Chess</strong>, you become another piece on the world's board, but with a difference: You are special, you have a vision of the board, you know the rules and you know exactly what to do: <strong> DESTROY ENEMIES!</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-DestroyPiece.gif?t=1708607743\" /><br><br>You start as a simple piece that can move one square to each side, but each round, you can buy a card to gain abilities that range from moving one more square at a time to attacking from a distance or an extra life.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-CardsView.gif?t=1708607743\" /><br><br>Customize your game with the various skins from the store purchased with money purchased within the game:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-Shop.gif?t=1708607743\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-SkinsPlayer.gif?t=1708607743\" /><br><br>Improve your strategy, think about each move and advance as much as you can by facing more pieces through turns:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-DestroyPiece2.gif?t=1708607743\" /><br><br>Choose the scenario you want as the battlefield:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-RoomView.gif?t=1708607743\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/extras/Gif-BeachView.gif?t=1708607743\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1708607743","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/